original: A rugged full-length duster coat.  Has many pockets for storage.
translation: 粗犷的全长掸子大衣。有许多口袋可供存放。

original: A bandolier, strapped onto the arm, that can contain several bomlets for ease of access.
translation: 一种绑在手臂上的带子，可以装几个带子以便于取用。

original: A fluid bladder from a plant based lifeform.  Not very nutritious, and may play host to microscopic germs.
translation: 植物生命体的液体囊。营养不良，可能是微生物的宿主。

original: This is an firebomb fitted into a manhack and rigged so the manhack can self-activate it.  This one is active.
translation: 这是一个安装在检修孔内的燃烧弹，并被操纵，以便检修孔能自动激活它。这个是活动的。

original: A simple homemade launcher for bomblets, consisting of a wooden supports nailed to a length of piping and a modified stopper to hold and activate the bomblet.
translation: 一种简单的自制小炸弹发射器，由钉在一段管道上的木制支架和一个用来固定和启动小炸弹的改进的塞子组成。

original: a thickened water solution, primed to evaporate into smoke.  Probably safer not to consume
translation: 浓缩的水溶液，准备蒸发成烟。不吃可能更安全

original: Carl JR. appreciates your business.  Enjoy your order of 'EXTRA BIG-ASS FRIES'.  Please come back when you can afford to make another purchase of 'EXTRA BIG-ASS FRIES'.
translation: 小卡尔很欣赏你的生意。享受你点的“超级大屁股薯条”。请回来时，你可以再购买'额外的大屁股薯条'。

original: This is an acidbomb fitted into a manhack and rigged so the manhack can self-activate it.  Due to the manhack exploding the effective radius is somewhat larger.
translation: 这是一个酸弹安装在一个检修孔和操纵，使检修孔可以自我激活它。由于人孔爆炸，有效半径稍大。
优质可重复充装打火机

original: The nail sword, or nord for short.  This wooden sword has a dozen nails sticking at jagged angles from edge of the blade, making it much better at chopping than slashing.
translation: 指甲剑，简称诺德。这把木剑有一打钉子，从刀刃的边缘呈锯齿状，使它更善于砍而不是砍。

original: This is an ultra-light alcohol-burning stove with simmer ring, crafted by hand from a couple of aluminum soda cans.  It comes with a 250 ml plastic bottle to hold concentrated alcohol fuel.
translation: 这是一个超轻酒精燃烧炉与煨环，手工制作从一对铝苏打罐。它配有一个250毫升的塑料瓶，用来盛装浓缩酒精燃料。

original: This is a lighter that has been modified to output a larger flame than normal lighters.  While ideal for starting fires, and able to start them faster, it is a bit of a fuel hog, consuming it almost twice as fast.
translation: 这是一个打火机，已被修改，以输出比正常打火机更大的火焰。虽然它非常适合点火，而且能够更快地点火，但它有点耗油，消耗速度几乎是原来的两倍。

original: Spawns an tribot into the world.
translation: 在这个世界上诞生了一个摩托生物。

original: This is a home built launcher tube that can be attached to almost any rifle.  It allows a single 40mm grenade to be loaded and fired.
translation: 这是一个自制的发射管，可以连接到几乎任何步枪。它允许一个40毫米手榴弹加载和发射。

original: A lighter with a bit of string and taping to allow it to be worn about the neck like a lanyard.  A bit fumbly to get a hold of, but perfectly servicable.
translation: 一种打火机，带有一点细绳和带子，可以像系索一样系在脖子上。有点失手，但很好的服务。

original: An enormous mutant mosquito, fluttering erratically.  Its face is dominated by a long, spear-tipped proboscis.  It attempts to cling to large enough prey.
translation: 一种巨大的变异蚊子，不稳定地摆动。它的脸上长着一个尖尖的长鼻。它试图抓住足够大的猎物。

original: A colossal red ant with a bulging, bloated thorax.  It moves slowly and deliberately, tending to nearby eggs and continually laying more.  Its antennae seem almost aesthetic, or at the least not used for sensing . . .
translation: 一种巨大的红色蚂蚁，胸部膨胀。它缓慢而有意识地移动，倾向于附近的卵，并不断产卵。它的触角看起来很美，或者至少不用于感知。

original: A large humanoid shadow, chaotically changing in shape and volume , two piercing orbs of light dominate what can only be described as its head.
translation: 一个巨大的人形阴影，在形状和体积上混乱地变化，两个穿透的光球支配着它的头部。

original: A sickly yellow, elongated humanoid.  With almost complete control over its own flames it attacks with pyrokinesis and breathes life into fallen combatants.
translation: 一种病态的黄色、细长的人形动物。它几乎完全控制了自己的火焰，以高温攻击，并向倒下的战斗人员呼吸生命。

original: This humanoid resembles a burnt cenobite.  It attacks with fire and claw, and is the grunt of the demonic armies.
translation: 这个人形动物像一个被烧焦的牙齿。它用火和爪子攻击，是恶魔军队的呼噜声。

original: Just a tiny bird, quite cute
Spawns a cherub, little baby demon.
translation: 产下一个小天使，小恶魔。

original: A candle in every respect, but designed to produce a thin stream of smoke.  Often used in ceremonies or to add an air of 'ambient mystery', but could likely be used to reduce scent by windows and doors it is placed next to.
translation: 蜡烛各方面的一种蜡烛，但设计用来产生一股细烟。通常用于仪式或增加一种“神秘气氛”，但可能用于减少窗户和门旁边的气味。

original: A thick stalk with rapidly sprouting tendrils at the base and a 'crown' of deep magenta pitchers at its head.  The pitchers taper into o-rings, pointing at various angles away from the hub.  From the center of the crown stems a single large, mace-like tentacle that flails around menacingly.
translation: 一种粗茎，基部有迅速发芽的卷须，头上有深品红水罐的“树冠”。水罐逐渐变成o型环，指向远离轮毂的不同角度。从树冠的中心伸出一根巨大的、象狼牙棒一样的触须，凶猛地挥舞着。

original: The deformed, animated corpse of a canine, a sinewy beast which can easily outpace its two-legged friends.
translation: 狗的畸形的、有活力的尸体，一种强壮的野兽，很容易超过它的双腿朋友。

original: Spawns a flying cherub, little baby demon.
translation: 生一个会飞的小天使，小恶魔。

original: This smoking candle is lit, providing both aeromatic smoke and light.
translation: 点燃这根冒烟的蜡烛，提供空气烟雾和光。

original: "I detect a sudden rise in hubris in this region."
translation: “我发现这个地区的傲慢情绪突然上升。”
“我的孩子们，有一只船在旁边抛锚！”

original: "Paco can run his own damn meth next time.  Im done."
translation: “帕科下次可以自己开冰毒了。我做完了。”

original: "Multiple Core-system failures detected.  Diverting power from secondary personnel recognition software to weapons."
translation: “检测到多个核心系统故障。将次要人员识别软件的权力转移到武器上。”

original: "Weed, Meth, Coke n' crack, my pockets flowin' over out the back."
translation: “大麻，冰毒，可乐，我的口袋从后面流出来。”

original: a faint, high-pitched whining of engines
translation: 发动机发出微弱的、高亢的呜呜声
伤痕累累的小鬼产卵者

original: Spawns an scarred imp into the world.
translation: 把一个伤痕累累的小鬼带到这个世界上。

original: "Did you come here knowing you had a warrent out?"
translation: “你来这里是不是知道你有一场战争？”

original: "It puts the lotion on the skin, or else it breaks the skin again."
translation: “它把乳液涂在皮肤上，否则它又会把皮肤弄破。”

original: You put the lime in the coco nuts and shake your body round!
translation: 你把青柠放在椰子里，摇动你的身体！

original: "This is Autonomous Helicoptor Drone, Model 4751ZuluBeta, broadcasting its legal message, informing you of its authority under the joint Police-Military Statutes passed by the Executive Branch in 2034.  Under these statutes, lethal force is authorized."
translation: “这是自主直升机无人机，型号4751ZuluBeta，正在广播它的法律信息，告知你它在2034年行政部门通过的联合警察军事法规下的权力。根据这些法令，可以使用致命武力。”

original: what sounds like many robotic ants tunneling around.
translation: 听起来像是许多机器蚂蚁在挖隧道。

original: Rebalances spawn list, adds new monsters and items, adds new buildings and fortifies old buildings, and strives to create a harsher enviornment to survive in.
translation: 重新平衡繁殖列表，添加新怪物和物品，添加新建筑和加固旧建筑，并努力创造一个更严酷的环境中生存。

original: "To protect all essential personnel and equipment."
translation: “保护所有必要的人员和设备。”

original: "Sensors have indicated you J-walked several times within the past 5 days.  Public disorder is no excuse for criminal activity."
translation: “传感器显示你在过去5天内走了好几次。公共秩序混乱不是犯罪活动的借口。”

original: "1 shot 2 shot, this is where the fun stops"
"When the fourth wall is torn down, THEN!"
translation: “那么，当第四堵墙被拆掉的时候！”

original: "Bystanders not engaging in rebellious, treasonous, criminal, or conflict-like behavior are advised to enter a prone position, keeping their hands over their heads until the current crisis is over and authorized personel retrieve you for debriefing."
translation: “不从事叛逆、叛逆、犯罪或类似冲突行为的旁观者，建议进入俯卧姿势，将手放在头上，直到当前危机结束，并由授权人员接回你进行汇报。”

original: a clanking from under your feet.
The %1$s tries to impale your torso, but fails to penetrate your armor!
translation: %1$s试图刺穿你的躯干，但未能穿透你的盔甲！

translation: 这是一台蜡烛操作的烟雾机。打开后，它会在近处产生雾状烟雾，模糊视觉和气味。它可以随意关闭，但空的时候需要解构和重新构建。

original: The %1$s tries to impale <npcname>'s torso, but fails to penetrate their armor!
translation: %1$s试图刺穿<npcname>的躯干，但未能穿透他们的盔甲！

original: "Scanning ...  Xenos Life Patterns detected.  Irreversible levels of infection found.  Termination imminent."
translation: “正在扫描。。。检测到氙气生命模式。发现不可逆的感染水平。即将终止。”

original: "This area is off limits to non-law-efforcement personnel.  Leave immediately."
translation: “这个区域禁止非执法人员进入。马上离开。”

original: "Its not real, its not real, its all a bad dream."
translation: “不是真的，不是真的，都是噩梦。”

original: "when I find that little somnabitch, I'll show 'em who's boss"
translation: “当我找到那个小家伙，我会让他们知道谁是老大”

original: "'UZI' WHAT HAPPENS WHEN YOU MESS WITH ME?!!  HEHHeeehehHEE!"
"Children under the age of 4 should be held by their parent or guardian, and that person should be seen to have their hands clasped together away from their own person.
translation: “4岁以下的孩子应该由他们的父母或监护人抱着，而且应该看到这个人双手合十，远离自己的人。

original: "Le traducteur peut etre trouve au troisieme bureau a votre gauche"
"Sensors indicate an ongoing riot.  Return to your homes or be subject to arrest."
translation: “传感器显示正在发生骚乱。回到你的家里或者被逮捕。”

original: "Hey!  Im looking for some butter.  Got any?"
"I told her I'd give it back when I was done but Noooo, we had to play it hardball."
translation: “我告诉她我做完后会还给她，但是不行，我们得强硬些。”

original: "The elderly, or those otherwise incapable or achieving a prone position should prepare the proper form of ID in a readily viewable location and keep their hands out of all bags, pockets, or other concealed locations."
translation: 老年人或其他无能力或达到俯卧姿势的人，应在容易看见的地方准备适当的身份证，并将手放在所有袋子、口袋或其他隐蔽的地方

original: You are experiencing hallucinations.  The resulting sense of surrealism is a real stressor, and gets the blood pumping.
translation: 你在经历幻觉。由此产生的超现实主义是一个真正的压力源，并得到血液泵。

original: Spawns a scarred pink demon into the world.
translation: 把一个伤痕累累的粉色恶魔带到这个世界上。

original: The %1$s tries to strike you but fails.

translation: “纳斯尼亚达尼·兹贾德勒姆·兹耶科耶佐兹维耶兹”

original: "Halt!  You have violated the law.  Pay your fine or come with me."
translation: “站住！你触犯了法律。付你的罚款或者跟我来。”
反重力推进器的嗡嗡声！

original: the muffled sound of rock being blasted.
The %1$s tries to strike <npcname>, but fails to.
Looks dangerous, you could attach it to a vehicle.
translation: 看起来很危险，你可以把它绑在车上。

original: You can move more quickly than most, resulting in a 15% speed bonus on sure footing.
translation: 你可以比大多数人更快地移动，从而在稳固的基础上获得15%的速度加成。

original: Your body continuously struggles to keep up with your physiology.  You often feel less than perfect; and in need of remedy.
translation: 你的身体一直在努力跟上你的生理学。你常常觉得自己不够完美，需要补救。

original: "Olen vanhentunut taman paivan vaatimuksia. Tama tekee minut surulliseksi joten aion tappaa sinut"
translation: “奥伦·凡亨图努特·塔曼·帕万·瓦提穆克西亚。Tama tekee minut surulliseksi joten aion Tappa sinut“公司”

original: "I should have never gone hunting.  No money in it.  Gotta shoot me some people instead."
translation: “我不该去打猎。里面没钱。我得杀几个人。”

original: "This nature shit.  Ive got deerturds on my boots!"
translation: “这是大自然的大便。我的靴子上有帽子！”

original: the rush of thrusters as something gains elevation quickly.
translation: 当某物迅速上升时，推进器的冲击。

original: Something you have consumed was never meant for eating and contains heavy metals.
translation: 你吃过的东西不是用来吃的，而且含有重金属。

original: This is a candle-operated smoke machine.  When turned on it will produce a fog-like smoke in the immediete area, obscuring vision and scent.  It can be turned off at will, but when empty will need to be deconstructed and recrafted.  Use it once to set it up for use, then again to activate it.
translation: 这是一台蜡烛操作的烟雾机。打开后，它会在近处产生雾状烟雾，模糊视觉和气味。它可以随意关闭，但空的时候需要解构和重新构建。使用它一次设置使用，然后再次激活它。

original: "I am Cyberguard 47.  I can comprehend over 74 languages, and shoot speakers of every one of them."
translation: “我是Cyberguard 47。我能听懂74种以上的语言，而且每种语言我都能说。”

original: "Initiating self-repair preservation protocols.  Backing up data... ..."
translation: “启动自我修复保存协议。正在备份数据……”

original: "You see how I lit up that zombie?  So many holes I made it look like one of them fountain statues"
translation: “你看到我怎么点燃那僵尸了吗？我把它弄得像喷泉雕像一样

translation: “黄蜂接近继续Y黄蜂接近继续Y黄蜂接近继续Y黄蜂接近继续Y黄蜂接近黄蜂接近”

You have recently taken a Prussain Blue pill.  It will slowly cleanse your body of radiation; taking more will speed up the process.
translation: 你最近吃了普鲁士蓝药丸。它会慢慢清除你体内的辐射，多吃会加速这个过程。

original: An improvised shelter made by digging a pit one can shelter in and covering the top
translation: 一种临时的庇护所，通过挖一个可以遮蔽的坑并覆盖顶部而成

original: Having just torn a hole through hell itself, you stepped into a teleporter to find yourself... here.  Your radio is dead, you're out of supplies, and you're still knee-deep in the dead.  There's a whole new world to purge, but you see some old enemies ahead.
translation: 刚刚在地狱里挖了一个洞，你走进了传送机，发现自己。。。在这里。你的收音机没电了，你的补给也用完了，你还没死呢。有一个全新的世界需要净化，但你会看到前面有一些宿敌。

original: After defeating your foes in Hell you find they fled to Earth.
translation: 在地狱里打败你的敌人之后，你会发现他们逃到了地上。

original: Spawns a battered hell knight into the world.
translation: 在这个世界上诞生一个受尽折磨的地狱骑士。

original: "I am a guard cyborg, model T-1000B, serial number 467AlphaEpsilon954GammaZulu415BetaAlphaAlpha."
translation: “我是一个守卫机器人，型号T-1000B，序列号467alphaepsilon954Gammazul415betaalphaalpha。”

original: "You think a 'sick pack' is going to fix this?!"
translation: “你认为一个‘病包’能解决这个问题吗？！”

original: "I had no choice.  Better that kid than me anyway, how would he have lived?"
translation: “我别无选择。不管怎样，那孩子比我强，他会怎么活？”

original: "I'm dying for a leg of meat . . ."
"Shockcannons are good close defense turrets for a car, but may drain your batteries quickly."
translation: “防震炮对汽车来说是很好的近身防御炮塔，但可能会很快耗尽你的电池。”

original: You feel unhealthier for it, but the stims are gone at least.
translation: 你为此感到不健康，但至少刺激消失了。

original: "Spiders will kill an unprepared player.  Ants will kill an unprepared player.  Black rats will kill an unprepared player.  Sewer rats will kill an unprepared player.  Everything will kill an unprepared player."
translation: 蜘蛛会杀死一个没有准备的玩家。蚂蚁会杀死一个没有准备的玩家。黑鼠会杀死一个毫无准备的玩家。下水道老鼠会杀死一个没有准备的玩家。一切都会杀死一个毫无准备的玩家。”

original: "Oil Rig?  Wayda think I am, stupid or somethin'?"
translation: “石油钻塔？你以为我是傻瓜吗

original: "They told me it was safe, why would they lie to me?"
translation: “他们告诉我这是安全的，他们为什么要骗我？”

original: the ear-throbbing sound of a helidrones thrusters.
translation: 直升机推进器发出的震耳欲聋的声音。

original: You feel the stims start to tax you as they wear off.
translation: 你觉得刺激开始征税，因为他们磨损你。

original: You don't feel as badass as before.
translation: 你感觉不像以前那么糟了。

original: The rush takes you, Rip and Tear!

translation: “环境抵抗将失败者和幸存者分开。”

translation: 闻起来很难闻，你可以游过去。

original: You are a pointman for the statewide SWAT force.  You are dispatched in small groups to settle disputes that the politicians want handled with a more 'human' touch for public relations purposes.  Something spit gooey-hot acid all over your armor and mask, but you still have your shield and arbiter.
translation: 你是全州特警队的指挥员。你们被分成小组来解决政客们希望以更“人性化”的方式处理的公共关系纠纷。有什么东西在你的盔甲和面具上吐出粘糊糊的热酸，但你仍然有你的盾牌和仲裁者。

original: You were assigned to the last of the real riots; one of the last to flee when the rioters stopped breathing but kept moving.
translation: 你被指派参加最后一次真正的暴动；当暴动者停止呼吸，但继续移动时，你是最后一个逃跑的人。

original: "CONGRATULATIONS!  You are the 1000th person to read this note.  Press [Shift]+[Q]+[Y] to claim your prize now!"
translation: “恭喜！你是第1000个读这封信的人。按[Shift]+[Q]+[Y]立即领取奖品！”

original: "Gonna get me a chainsaw, strap it to my arm."
"So, what is this thing supposed to be, exactly?"
translation: “那么，这东西到底应该是什么？”

Your clothing and other equipment may be consumed by the flames.
translation:
失去健康-全身
您的衣服和其他设备可能会被火焰吞噬。

original: "It would appear that the gas in those mines are radioactive.  Probably a bad idea to breathe it in."
translation: “这些矿井中的气体似乎具有放射性。吸入可能是个坏主意。”

original: You defensively repose yourself as you attack
translation: 当你进攻时，你防守性地休息

original: "I saw a family of spiders slip out from under this medium boulder and drag my friends down below.  They had some good stuff on them too; I bet it's still down there."
translation: “我看到一群蜘蛛从这块中等大小的石头下面溜出来，把我的朋友拖到下面。他们身上也带了些好东西，我敢打赌还在下面。”

original: "I had a dog and his name was BLUUE!"

translation: “我在生活中找到了我的梦想。“会合”

original: "triffid sacs can be treated with a little cooking skill and made useful with a little tailoring skill"
translation: “三趾囊可以用一点烹饪技巧来治疗，也可以用一点裁剪技巧变得有用”

original: Spawns an abhorrent cacodemon into the world.

original: "Subject has so far displayed a total lack of empathy toward human suffering."
translation: “到目前为止，研究对象对人类的苦难完全缺乏同情心。”

original: "Only a few more days 'til the weekend."
Spawns a very rude acidic zombie.
translation: 产生一个非常粗鲁的酸性僵尸。

original: "You got a dollar I can borrow?"
"Are you going to the party tonight?"
"I think I need to see a doctor."
"We should hit up the shooting range later."
"I'm heading to the pool after work."
"I got this weird rash a few days ago."
translation: “几天前我得了这种奇怪的皮疹。”

original: "Let me have a look at it."
"We should split into groups of two each."
translation: "我们应该分成两组，每组两个人。"

original: "I've been looking all over for you."
"Take his gun, we're going to need it."
"How do we get out of here?"
"Oh God, I'm the only one left."
